{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775875938459,"sessionID":"ses_2858e9b85ffetfq8oC43JXMakK","part":{"id":"prt_d7a716d63001bO8zKmPknQMkvx","messageID":"msg_d7a716566001HK06fKoKCFkBFA","sessionID":"ses_2858e9b85ffetfq8oC43JXMakK","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_a398ee6cbdb64cd8add07979","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore agentcube project","prompt":"Explore the agentcube project thoroughly. I need to understand:\n1. The overall project structure - what directories exist, what files are present\n2. Any existing Dockerfile or docker-related files\n3. Any design documents, specs, or documentation about the Docker multi-stage build\n4. The main application structure - what services/components exist that need to be containerized\n5. Any existing docker-compose files\n6. Look for any ST-3 or ST-4 design documents\n7. Check for any AR-032 related documentation\n\nSearch in the current working directory and all subdirectories. Be very thorough - check docs/, design/, specs/, any markdown files, and the project root.\n\nReturn a comprehensive summary of:\n- Project structure (key directories and files)\n- What the application does (based on code/docs)\n- Any existing Docker configuration\n- Any design/spec documents related to Docker multi-stage builds\n- What 3 images are needed and what each should contain","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_2858e8137ffeHPhpPz285hdi2j (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nI now have a thorough understanding of the entire project. Here is the comprehensive summary:\n\n---\n\n## Comprehensive Project Summary: AgentCube\n\n### 1. Project Overview\n\n**AgentCube** is a Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents. It provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic to them through session-aware proxies, and manages their full lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup).\n\n**Source:** `github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube`\n**Go Module:** `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`\n**Go Version:** 1.25.0\n\n---\n\n### 2. Project Structure (Key Directories and Files)\n\n```\n(project root)\n├── cmd/                          # Go binary entry points\n│   ├── workloadmanager/          # Workload Manager binary (K8s controller + HTTP API)\n│   ├── router/                   # Router binary (HTTP reverse proxy / session router)\n│   ├── picod/                    # PicoD binary (sandbox execution daemon)\n│   ├── agentd/                   # AgentD binary (idle cleanup controller)\n│   └── cli/                      # Python CLI tool\n├── pkg/                          # Shared Go packages\n│   ├── apis/                     # CRD type definitions\n│   │   ├── agents/v1alpha1/      # Sandbox types\n│   │   └── runtime/v1alpha1/     # CodeInterpreter, AgentRuntime types\n│   ├── workloadmanager/          # WM handlers, reconcilers, response helpers\n│   ├── router/                   # Router server logic\n│   ├── picod/                    # PicoD server logic\n│   ├── agentd/                   # AgentD reconciler\n│   ├── store/                    # Redis/Valkey session store\n│   └── common/                   # Shared types\n├── client-go/                    # Generated Kubernetes clientset/informers/listers\n├── manifests/                    # Helm charts and CRDs\n│   └── charts/base/              # Helm chart (templates, CRDs, values)\n├── changes/                      # Change request archives (AR-001 through AR-032)\n│   └── AR-032/                   # **Docker multi-stage build change**\n│       ├── proposal.md\n│       ├── design.md\n│       ├── delta-spec.md\n│       └── tasks.md\n├── deployment/                   # Deployment design and spec\n│   ├── design.md                 # Detailed Helm chart, Dockerfiles, Makefile reference\n│   └── spec.md                   # Deployment requirements\n├── python-sdk/                   # Python SDK (agentcube package)\n├── go.mod / go.sum               # Go module files\n├── (NO docker/ directory)        # **Does not exist yet - needs to be created**\n└── (NO Makefile)                 # Referenced in docs but not present in this working copy\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. What the Application Does\n\nThe system has **4 main Go binaries** and a **Python SDK/CLI**:\n\n| Binary | Purpose | Port | Health Endpoint |\n|--------|---------|------|-----------------|\n| **workloadmanager** | Kubernetes controller managing agent-sandbox lifecycle; HTTP API for creating/deleting/listing sandboxes | 8080 | `/health/live`, `/health/ready` |\n| **agentcube-router** | HTTP reverse proxy/session router; routes requests to correct sandbox pods; manages JWT auth and session store (Redis/Valkey) | 8080 | `/health/live`, `/health/ready` |\n| **picod** | Sandbox-internal execution daemon; manages code interpreter sessions inside sandbox pods | None (internal) | None |\n| **agentd** | Idle cleanup controller; watches Sandbox CRs and cleans up idle/expired sandboxes | None (controller) | None |\n\n**Architecture Flow:**\n```\nClient / SDK / CLI\n  -> Router (Deployment :8080)\n     <-> Redis/Valkey (session store)\n     -> WorkloadManager (Service :8080)\n        <-> Redis/Valkey\n        -> K8s API: CRDs, Sandbox, Pod, Secret, TokenReview\n  Sandbox Pods (with optional PicoD daemon)\n  Agentd (idle cleanup controller)\n  Optional: Volcano vc-agent-scheduler\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4. Existing Docker Configuration\n\n**No Dockerfile or docker-related files currently exist in the project.** Specifically:\n- No `Dockerfile` files found anywhere\n- No `docker-compose` files found anywhere\n- No `docker/` directory exists (confirmed by `ls` returning empty)\n- The `deployment/design.md` references Dockerfiles that should exist at `docker/Dockerfile`, `docker/Dockerfile.router`, and `docker/Dockerfile.picod` but they are not yet created\n- The Makefile (not present in this working copy but documented) has `docker-build`, `docker-build-router`, and `docker-build-picod` targets that reference these non-existent Dockerfiles\n\n---\n\n### 5. AR-032 Design Documents (Docker Multi-Stage Build)\n\nThe **AR-032** change request is the definitive specification for the Docker multi-stage build. It contains four documents:\n\n| File | Location | Purpose |\n|------|----------|---------|\n| **proposal.md** | `changes/AR-032/proposal.md` | Skeleton proposal (TODO placeholders) |\n| **design.md** | `changes/AR-032/design.md` | Full design document (506 lines) - architecture, data structures, API contracts, error handling, testing strategy, implementation steps |\n| **delta-spec.md** | `changes/AR-032/delta-spec.md` | Detailed requirements in Given/When/Then format (151 lines) |\n| **tasks.md** | `changes/AR-032/tasks.md` | Implementation task checklist with acceptance criteria (176 lines) |\n\n**Key findings from AR-032:**\n- **Status:** Design stage (ST-3) is complete; implementation has NOT started\n- **Dependency:** None (greenfield -- `docker/` directory does not exist yet)\n- **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n\n---\n\n### 6. ST-3 and ST-4 References\n\n- **ST-3** = Design stage. All change requests (AR-001 through AR-032) reference ST-3 as a precondition for implementation tasks.\n- **ST-4** = Implementation stage. Only AR-001 and AR-008 are marked as ST-4 (already in implementation).\n- **AR-032** is at ST-3 (Design Complete) -- ready for implementation but not yet started.\n\n---\n\n### 7. The 3 Docker Images Needed\n\nBased on AR-032 design.md, delta-spec.md, tasks.md, and deployment/design.md, here are the exact specifications:\n\n#### Image 1: Workload Manager (`docker/Dockerfile`)\n\n| Attribute | Value |\n|-----------|-------|\n| **Binary** | `workloadmanager` |\n| **Source** | `./cmd/workloadmanager` |\n| **Builder Base** | `golang:1.25-alpine` |\n| **Runtime Base** | `alpine:3.19` |\n| **Runtime Packages** | `ca-certificates` |\n| **Non-root User** | `apiserver` (UID 1000) |\n| **EXPOSE** | `8080` |\n| **ENTRYPOINT** | `[\"/app/workloadmanager\"]` |\n| **CMD** | `[\"--port=8080\"]` |\n| **Build Flags** | `CGO_ENABLED=0`, `GOOS=${TARGETOS}`, `GOARCH=${TARGETARCH}`, `-ldflags=\"-s -w\"` |\n| **Extra COPY** | None |\n| **Expected Size** | < 50 MB |\n| **Health Endpoint** | `GET /health` on port 8080 |\n\n#### Image 2: Router (`docker/Dockerfile.router`)\n\n| Attribute | Value |\n|-----------|-------|\n| **Binary** | `agentcube-router` |\n| **Source** | `./cmd/router` |\n| **Builder Base** | `golang:1.25-alpine` |\n| **Runtime Base** | `alpine:3.19` |\n| **Runtime Packages** | `ca-certificates` |\n| **Non-root User** | `router` (UID 1000) |\n| **EXPOSE** | `8080` |\n| **ENTRYPOINT** | `[\"/app/agentcube-router\"]` |\n| **CMD** | `[\"--port=8080\", \"--debug\"]` |\n| **Build Flags** | `CGO_ENABLED=0`, `GOOS=${TARGETOS}`, `GOARCH=${TARGETARCH}`, `-ldflags=\"-s -w\"` |\n| **Extra COPY** | `COPY client-go/ client-go/` (generated K8s client) |\n| **Expected Size** | < 50 MB |\n| **Health Endpoints** | `GET /health/live`, `GET /health/ready` on port 8080 |\n\n#### Image 3: PicoD (`docker/Dockerfile.picod`)\n\n| Attribute | Value |\n|-----------|-------|\n| **Binary** | `picod` |\n| **Source** | `./cmd/picod` |\n| **Builder Base** | `golang:1.25-alpine` |\n| **Runtime Base** | `alpine:3.19` |\n| **Runtime Packages** | `python3` (code interpreter runtime) |\n| **Non-root User** | `picod` (UID 1000) |\n| **EXPOSE** | None (runs inside sandbox pods) |\n| **ENTRYPOINT** | `[\"/app/picod\"]` |\n| **CMD** | None (ENTRYPOINT only) |\n| **Build Flags** | `CGO_ENABLED=0`, `GOOS=${TARGETOS}`, `GOARCH=${TARGETARCH}`, `-ldflags=\"-s -w\"` |\n| **Extra COPY** | None |\n| **Expected Size** | < 100 MB (larger due to python3) |\n| **Health Endpoint** | None |\n\n---\n\n### 8. Multi-Stage Build Pattern (All 3 Dockerfiles)\n\nEach Dockerfile follows this uniform two-stage pattern:\n\n```\nStage 1: builder\n  Base: golang:1.25-alpine\n  1. WORKDIR /workspace\n  2. COPY go.mod go.sum ./\n  3. RUN go mod download\n  4. COPY cmd/ pkg/ [client-go/] ./\n  5. RUN CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=${TARGETOS} GOARCH=${TARGETARCH} go build -ldflags=\"-s -w\" -o /<binary> ./cmd/<entrypoint>\n\nStage 2: runtime\n  Base: alpine:3.19\n  1. apk add ca-certificates (or python3 for PicoD)\n  2. WORKDIR /app\n  3. COPY --from=builder /<binary> /app/<binary>\n  4. RUN adduser -D -u 1000 <user>\n  5. USER <user>\n  6. EXPOSE 8080 (WM and Router only)\n  7. ENTRYPOINT [\"/app/<binary>\"]\n  8. CMD [...] (WM and Router only)\n```\n\n---\n\n### 9. `.dockerignore` Requirements\n\nThe `docker/.dockerignore` file must exclude:\n```\n.git\n.gitignore\ntest/\ntesting/\nsdk-python/\ndocs/\ncoverage.out\n.pytest_cache/\n.coverage\n*.md\n!README.md\n```\n\n---\n\n### 10. Key File Paths (Absolute)\n\n**AR-032 Design Documents:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-032/design.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-032/delta-spec.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-032/tasks.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-032/proposal.md`\n\n**Deployment Reference:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/deployment/design.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/deployment/spec.md`\n\n**Source Entry Points:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/workloadmanager/main.go`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/router/main.go`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/picod/main.go`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/agentd/main.go`\n\n**Module Files:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/go.mod`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/go.sum`\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_2858e8137ffeHPhpPz285hdi2j","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project","time":{"start":1775875751622,"end":1775875938456}}}}
