{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775875941873,"sessionID":"ses_2858e9b85ffetfq8oC43JXMakK","part":{"id":"prt_d7a7462140011qilHy8IEtR3mb","messageID":"msg_d7a7458fe001EP9qZCZ4T7mW2J","sessionID":"ses_2858e9b85ffetfq8oC43JXMakK","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_701308b8f2f94e44ac29277d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-032/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-032/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-032: Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images) — Design/设计说明\n2: \n3: ## 1. 架构 (Architecture)\n4: \n5: ### 1.1 定位 (Purpose/Positioning)\n6: \n7: 本变更为 AgentCube 项目创建三个独立的多阶段 Dockerfile，用于构建生产级容器镜像：\n8: \n9: | Dockerfile | 二进制 | 用途 |\n10: |------------|--------|------|\n11: | `docker/Dockerfile` | `workloadmanager` | Workload Manager — Kubernetes 控制器，管理 agent-sandbox 沙箱生命周期 |\n12: | `docker/Dockerfile.router` | `agentcube-router` | Router — HTTP 反向代理/会话路由器，将请求路由到正确的沙箱 |\n13: | `docker/Dockerfile.picod` | `picod` | PicoD — 沙箱内执行守护进程，负责代码解释器会话管理 |\n14: \n15: 每个 Dockerfile 遵循统一的多阶段构建模式：Go 编译阶段 → 最小运行时阶段。构建产物为静态链接的二进制文件（`CGO_ENABLED=0`），运行时镜像仅包含 Alpine 3.19 基础层和编译后的二进制，不包含 Go 工具链、源码或构建缓存。\n16: \n17: ### 1.2 目录结构 (Directory Layout)\n18: \n19: **当前状态 (Before):**\n20: \n21: ```\n22: (project root)\n23: ├── cmd/\n24: │   ├── workloadmanager/    # Workload Manager 入口\n25: │   ├── router/             # Router 入口\n26: │   ├── picod/              # PicoD 入口\n27: │   ├── agentd/             # AgentD 入口 (暂无 Dockerfile)\n28: │   └── cli/                # CLI 工具 (无需 Dockerfile)\n29: ├── pkg/                    # 共享 Go 包\n30: ├── client-go/              # 生成的 Kubernetes 客户端\n31: ├── Makefile                # docker-build 目标引用不存在的 docker/Dockerfile\n32: └── (无 docker/ 目录)\n33: ```\n34: \n35: **目标状态 (After):**\n36: \n37: ```\n38: (project root)\n39: ├── docker/\n40: │   ├── Dockerfile           # Workload Manager 多阶段构建\n41: │   ├── Dockerfile.router    # Router 多阶段构建\n42: │   ├── Dockerfile.picod     # PicoD 多阶段构建\n43: │   └── .dockerignore        # 构建上下文排除规则\n44: ├── cmd/                     # 不变\n45: ├── pkg/                     # 不变\n46: └── client-go/               # 不变\n47: ```\n48: \n49: ### 1.3 依赖关系 (Dependencies)\n50: \n51: ```\n52: AR-032 Dockerfile 多阶段构建\n53:   ├── 前置依赖\n54:   │   ├── Go 1.25.0 工具链 (golang:1.25-alpine)     # 编译阶段\n55:   │   ├── go.mod / go.sum                            # 依赖锁定文件\n56:   │   ├── cmd/workloadmanager/                       # WM 源码入口\n57:   │   ├── cmd/router/                                # Router 源码入口\n58:   │   ├── cmd/picod/                                 # PicoD 源码入口\n59:   │   ├── pkg/                                       # 共享包\n60:   │   └── client-go/                                 # 生成的 K8s 客户端 (Router 需要)\n61:   │\n62:   ├── 运行时依赖\n63:   │   ├── Alpine 3.19 (alpine:3.19)                  # WM / Router 运行时基础镜像\n64:   │   ├── Alpine 3.19 (alpine:3.19)                  # PicoD 运行时基础镜像\n65:   │   ├── ca-certificates                            # TLS 证书链 (WM / Router)\n66:   │   └── python3                                    # PicoD 代码解释器运行时\n67:   │\n68:   └── 构建工具\n69:       ├── docker build                               # 镜像构建\n70:       ├── Makefile docker-build 目标                  # 构建入口\n71:       └── BuildKit cache mounts                      # 层缓存优化\n72: ```\n73: \n74: ### 1.4 多阶段构建模式 (Multi-Stage Build Pattern)\n75: \n76: 所有三个 Dockerfile 遵循统一的两阶段模式：\n77: \n78: ```\n79: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐\n80: │  Stage 1: builder (编译阶段)             │\n81: │  ─────────────────────────────────────  │\n82: │  Base: golang:1.25-alpine               │\n83: │  1. WORKDIR /workspace                  │\n84: │  2. COPY go.mod go.sum ./               │\n85: │  3. RUN go mod download                 │\n86: │  4. COPY cmd/ pkg/ [client-go/] ./      │\n87: │  5. RUN CGO_ENABLED=0 go build ...      │\n88: │     → 产出: /<binary> (静态 Linux 二进制) │\n89: └──────────────────┬──────────────────────┘\n90:                    │ COPY --from=builder\n91:                    ▼\n92: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐\n93: │  Stage 2: runtime (运行时阶段)            │\n94: │  ─────────────────────────────────────  │\n95: │  Base: alpine:3.19                      │\n96: │  1. apk add ca-certificates (或 python3) │\n97: │  2. WORKDIR /app                        │\n98: │  3. COPY --from=builder /<binary> ./    │\n99: │  4. adduser -D -u 1000 <user>           │\n100: │  5. USER <user>                         │\n101: │  6. EXPOSE 8080 (WM / Router)           │\n102: │  7. ENTRYPOINT [\"/app/<binary>\"]        │\n103: └─────────────────────────────────────────┘\n104: ```\n105: \n106: ---\n107: \n108: ## 2. 数据结构 (Data Structures)\n109: \n110: ### 2.1 三镜像构建参数矩阵\n111: \n112: | 参数 | Dockerfile (WM) | Dockerfile.router | Dockerfile.picod |\n113: |------|-----------------|-------------------|------------------|\n114: | **Builder Base** | `golang:1.25-alpine` | `golang:1.25-alpine` | `golang:1.25-alpine` |\n115: | **Runtime Base** | `alpine:3.19` | `alpine:3.19` | `alpine:3.19` |\n116: | **Binary Source** | `./cmd/workloadmanager` | `./cmd/router` | `./cmd/picod` |\n117: | **Output Binary** | `workloadmanager` | `agentcube-router` | `picod` |\n118: | **Extra COPY** | 无 | `client-go/ client-go/` | 无 |\n119: | **Runtime Packages** | `ca-certificates` | `ca-certificates` | `python3` |\n120: | **Non-root User** | `apiserver` (UID 1000) | `router` (UID 1000) | `picod` (UID 1000) |\n121: | **EXPOSE** | `8080` | `8080` | 无 (sandbox 内执行) |\n122: | **ENTRYPOINT** | `[\"/app/workloadmanager\"]` | `[\"/app/agentcube-router\"]` | `[\"/app/picod\"]` |\n123: | **CMD** | `[\"--port=8080\"]` | `[\"--port=8080\", \"--debug\"]` | 无 (ENTRYPOINT only) |\n124: | **Build Flags** | `-ldflags=\"-s -w\"` | `-ldflags=\"-s -w\"` | `-ldflags=\"-s -w\"` |\n125: | **GOOS/GOARCH** | `${TARGETOS}/${TARGETARCH}` | `${TARGETOS}/${TARGETARCH}` | `${TARGETOS}/${TARGETARCH}` |\n126: \n127: ### 2.2 Build Args 定义\n128: \n129: | Build Arg | 默认值 | 用途 | 适用镜像 |\n130: |-----------|--------|------|---------|\n131: | `TARGETOS` | `linux` | 目标操作系统 | 全部 |\n132: | `TARGETARCH` | (平台自动) | 目标 CPU 架构 | 全部 |\n133: \n134: ### 2.3 .dockerignore 排除规则\n135: \n136: ```\n137: .git\n138: .gitignore\n139: test/\n140: testing/\n141: sdk-python/\n142: docs/\n143: coverage.out\n144: .pytest_cache/\n145: .coverage\n146: *.md\n147: !README.md\n148: ```\n149: \n150: 排除规则确保构建上下文不包含测试代码、Python SDK、文档、覆盖率报告和 pytest 缓存，减少上下文传输体积并避免将非构建产物纳入镜像。\n151: \n152: ### 2.4 层缓存策略\n153: \n154: 每个 Dockerfile 使用以下层缓存优化：\n155: \n156: ```dockerfile\n157: # Layer 1: 仅复制模块文件 (变化频率低)\n158: COPY go.mod go.sum ./\n159: RUN --mount=type=cache,target=/go/pkg/mod \\\n160:     go mod download\n161: \n162: # Layer 2: 复制源码 (变化频率高)\n163: COPY cmd/ cmd/\n164: COPY pkg/ pkg/\n165: # (Router 额外)\n166: COPY client-go/ client-go/\n167: \n168: # Layer 3: 编译\n169: RUN --mount=type=cache,target=/go/pkg/mod \\\n170:     --mount=type=cache,target=/root/.cache/go-build \\\n171:     CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=${TARGETOS} GOARCH=${TARGETARCH} \\\n172:     go build -ldflags=\"-s -w\" -o <binary> ./cmd/<entrypoint>\n173: ```\n174: \n175: `--mount=type=cache` 为 BuildKit 指令，需要 `DOCKER_BUILDKIT=1` 环境变量或 `docker buildx`。\n176: \n177: ---\n178: \n179: ## 3. API 契约 (API Contracts)\n180: \n181: ### 3.1 构建契约 (Build Contracts)\n182: \n183: #### 3.1.1 Workload Manager Dockerfile\n184: \n185: 文件: `docker/Dockerfile`\n186: \n187: 构建命令:\n188: ```bash\n189: docker build -f docker/Dockerfile -t workloadmanager:latest .\n190: ```\n191: \n192: 契约保证:\n193: \n194: | 契约项 | 保证 |\n195: |--------|------|\n196: | 构建上下文 | 仓库根目录 (`.`) |\n197: | Builder 阶段 | 使用 `golang:1.25-alpine`，`CGO_ENABLED=0` |\n198: | 编译目标 | `./cmd/workloadmanager` → `/workloadmanager` |\n199: | 运行时基础 | `alpine:3.19` |\n200: | 二进制拷贝 | `COPY --from=builder /workloadmanager /app/workloadmanager` |\n201: | 非 root 用户 | `adduser -D -u 1000 apiserver` + `USER apiserver` |\n202: | 暴露端口 | `EXPOSE 8080` |\n203: | 入口点 | `ENTRYPOINT [\"/app/workloadmanager\"]` |\n204: | 默认命令 | `CMD [\"--port=8080\"]` |\n205: | 仅含必要文件 | 无 Go 源码、无 go.mod、无构建缓存 |\n206: \n207: #### 3.1.2 Router Dockerfile\n208: \n209: 文件: `docker/Dockerfile.router`\n210: \n211: 构建命令:\n212: ```bash\n213: docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.router -t agentcube-router:latest .\n214: ```\n215: \n216: 契约保证:\n217: \n218: | 契约项 | 保证 |\n219: |--------|------|\n220: | 构建上下文 | 仓库根目录 (`.`) |\n221: | Builder 阶段 | 使用 `golang:1.25-alpine`，`CGO_ENABLED=0` |\n222: | 额外 COPY | `COPY client-go/ client-go/` (生成的 K8s 客户端) |\n223: | 编译目标 | `./cmd/router` → `/agentcube-router` |\n224: | 运行时基础 | `alpine:3.19` |\n225: | 非 root 用户 | `adduser -D -u 1000 router` + `USER router` |\n226: | 暴露端口 | `EXPOSE 8080` |\n227: | 入口点 | `ENTRYPOINT [\"/app/agentcube-router\"]` |\n228: | 默认命令 | `CMD [\"--port=8080\", \"--debug\"]` |\n229: \n230: #### 3.1.3 PicoD Dockerfile\n231: \n232: 文件: `docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n233: \n234: 构建命令:\n235: ```bash\n236: docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.picod -t picod:latest .\n237: ```\n238: \n239: 契约保证:\n240: \n241: | 契约项 | 保证 |\n242: |--------|------|\n243: | 构建上下文 | 仓库根目录 (`.`) |\n244: | Builder 阶段 | 使用 `golang:1.25-alpine`，`CGO_ENABLED=0` |\n245: | 编译目标 | `./cmd/picod` → `/picod` |\n246: | 运行时基础 | `alpine:3.19` |\n247: | 运行时包 | `python3` (代码解释器需要) |\n248: | 非 root 用户 | `adduser -D -u 1000 picod` + `USER picod` |\n249: | 暴露端口 | 无 (sandbox 内执行，不需对外暴露) |\n250: | 入口点 | `ENTRYPOINT [\"/app/picod\"]` |\n251: | 默认命令 | 无 (ENTRYPOINT 足够) |\n252: \n253: ### 3.2 Makefile 集成契约\n254: \n255: Makefile 中的 docker-build 目标 SHALL 引用新创建的 Dockerfile：\n256: \n257: | Makefile 目标 | Dockerfile | 镜像标签 |\n258: |---------------|------------|---------|\n259: | `docker-build` | `docker/Dockerfile` | `$(WORKLOAD_MANAGER_IMAGE)` = `workloadmanager:latest` |\n260: | `docker-build-router` | `docker/Dockerfile.router` | `$(ROUTER_IMAGE)` = `agentcube-router:latest` |\n261: | `docker-build-picod` | `docker/Dockerfile.picod` | `$(PICOD_IMAGE)` = `picod:latest` |\n262: \n263: ### 3.3 镜像元数据契约\n264: \n265: | 元数据项 | WorkloadManager | Router | PicoD |\n266: |----------|-----------------|--------|-------|\n267: | 运行时用户 UID | 1000 | 1000 | 1000 |\n268: | 运行时用户 GID | 1000 | 1000 | 1000 |\n269: | 工作目录 | `/app` | `/app` | `/app` |\n270: | 二进制路径 | `/app/workloadmanager` | `/app/agentcube-router` | `/app/picod` |\n271: | 健康检查端点 | `GET /health` (port 8080) | `GET /health/live` (port 8080) | 无 (sandbox 内) |\n272: \n273: ---\n274: \n275: ## 4. 错误处理 (Error Handling)\n276: \n277: ### 4.1 构建阶段错误\n278: \n279: | 场景 | 表现 | 处理方式 |\n280: |------|------|----------|\n281: | `go.mod`/`go.sum` 不存在 | `go mod download` 失败，构建退出码非 0 | 构建前确保模块文件存在于仓库根目录 |\n282: | 依赖下载失败 (网络问题) | `go mod download` 超时或 404 | BuildKit cache mount 可缓存已下载的模块；重试构建 |\n283: | 编译错误 (源码问题) | `go build` 失败，输出编译错误信息 | 修复源码后重新构建；`go build` 本地验证 |\n284: | 目标路径不存在 | `COPY --from=builder` 找不到二进制 | 确保 builder 阶段的输出路径与 runtime 阶段的 COPY 源路径一致 |\n285: | BuildKit 不可用 | `--mount=type=cache` 被忽略或报错 | 设置 `DOCKER_BUILDKIT=1`；降级到无 cache mount 的构建 |\n286: \n287: ### 4.2 运行时错误\n288: \n289: | 场景 | 表现 | 处理方式 |\n290: |------|------|----------|\n291: | 二进制以 root 运行 | 容器启动失败 (如果部署平台强制 non-root) | Dockerfile 已强制 `USER <non-root>`；Kubernetes PodSecurity 策略可作为额外保障 |\n292: | 端口冲突 | 二进制绑定 8080 失败 | 通过 CMD 参数 `--port=<other>` 覆盖；Kubernetes Service 端口映射解耦 |\n293: | 缺少 ca-certificates | TLS 连接 K8s API Server 失败 | 运行时阶段已 `apk add ca-certificates` |\n294: | PicoD 缺少 python3 | 代码解释器会话无法启动 | PicoD Dockerfile 已 `apk add python3` |\n295: | 镜像过大 | 包含不必要的文件 | `.dockerignore` 排除非构建文件；多阶段构建确保仅拷贝二进制 |\n296: \n297: ### 4.3 边界情况处理\n298: \n299: | 场景 | 处理 |\n300: |------|------|\n301: | 跨平台构建 (arm64) | `TARGETARCH` build arg 传递；`GOARCH=${TARGETARCH}` 在编译时使用 |\n302: | Docker 构建上下文过大 | `.dockerignore` 排除 `.git`、`test/`、`docs/` 等大目录 |\n303: | 镜像 digest 固定 | 生产环境可将 `alpine:3.19` 替换为 digest-pinned 版本 (如 `alpine@sha256:...`) |\n304: | 安全漏洞扫描 | 构建后可通过 `trivy` 或 `grype` 扫描镜像；Alpine 3.19 为当前 LTS |\n305: \n306: ---\n307: \n308: ## 5. 测试策略 (Testing Strategy)\n309: \n310: ### 5.1 静态验证 (Static Validation)\n311: \n312: #### 5.1.1 Dockerfile 语法检查\n313: \n314: ```bash\n315: # 使用 hadolint 检查 Dockerfile 最佳实践\n316: hadolint docker/Dockerfile\n317: hadolint docker/Dockerfile.router\n318: hadolint docker/Dockerfile.picod\n319: ```\n320: \n321: 预期：无 error 级问题，允许 info 级建议。\n322: \n323: #### 5.1.2 .dockerignore 验证\n324: \n325: ```bash\n326: # 验证构建上下文大小 (应远小于仓库总大小)\n327: docker build -f docker/Dockerfile --progress=plain . 2>&1 | grep \"transferring context\"\n328: ```\n329: \n330: ### 5.2 构建测试 (Build Tests)\n331: \n332: #### 5.2.1 镜像构建成功\n333: \n334: | 镜像 | 命令 | 断言 |\n335: |------|------|------|\n336: | WorkloadManager | `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile -t wm:test .` | 退出码 0，输出 `naming to docker.io/library/wm:test` |\n337: | Router | `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.router -t router:test .` | 退出码 0 |\n338: | PicoD | `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.picod -t picod:test .` | 退出码 0 |\n339: \n340: #### 5.2.2 镜像内容验证\n341: \n342: ```bash\n343: # 检查镜像中是否包含 Go 工具链 (不应存在)\n344: docker run --rm wm:test which go 2>/dev/null && echo \"FAIL: go found\" || echo \"PASS: no go\"\n345: \n346: # 检查二进制是否存在\n347: docker run --rm wm:test ls -la /app/workloadmanager\n348: docker run --rm router:test ls -la /app/agentcube-router\n349: docker run --rm picod:test ls -la /app/picod\n350: ```\n351: \n352: | 断言 | WorkloadManager | Router | PicoD |\n353: |------|-----------------|--------|-------|\n354: | 无 Go 工具链 | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |\n355: | 无 Go 源码 | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |\n356: | 二进制存在 | `/app/workloadmanager` | `/app/agentcube-router` | `/app/picod` |\n357: | ca-certificates 存在 | ✅ | ✅ | N/A |\n358: | python3 存在 | N/A | N/A | ✅ |\n359: \n360: ### 5.3 运行时测试 (Runtime Tests)\n361: \n362: #### 5.3.1 非 root 用户验证\n363: \n364: ```bash\n365: # 检查有效 UID\n366: docker run --rm wm:test id -u   # 期望: 1000\n367: docker run --rm router:test id -u  # 期望: 1000\n368: docker run --rm picod:test id -u   # 期望: 1000\n369: ```\n370: \n371: | 镜像 | 期望用户 | 期望 UID |\n372: |------|---------|---------|\n373: | WorkloadManager | `apiserver` | 1000 |\n374: | Router | `router` | 1000 |\n375: | PicoD | `picod` | 1000 |\n376: \n377: #### 5.3.2 端口暴露验证\n378: \n379: ```bash\n380: # WorkloadManager 健康检查\n381: docker run -d --name wm-test -p 8081:8080 wm:test\n382: sleep 2\n383: curl -s http://localhost:8081/health  # 期望: HTTP 200\n384: docker rm -f wm-test\n385: \n386: # Router 健康检查\n387: docker run -d --name router-test -p 8082:8080 router:test\n388: sleep 2\n389: curl -s http://localhost:8082/health/live  # 期望: HTTP 200\n390: docker rm -f router-test\n391: ```\n392: \n393: #### 5.3.3 镜像大小验证\n394: \n395: | 镜像 | 期望大小上限 | 说明 |\n396: |------|-------------|------|\n397: | WorkloadManager | < 50 MB | Alpine 3.19 (~7MB) + ca-certificates + 静态二进制 (~30MB) |\n398: | Router | < 50 MB | 同上 |\n399: | PicoD | < 100 MB | Alpine 3.19 + python3 (~40MB) + 静态二进制 (~30MB) |\n400: \n401: ```bash\n402: docker image inspect wm:test --format='{{.Size}}'  # 字节\n403: docker image inspect router:test --format='{{.Size}}'\n404: docker image inspect picod:test --format='{{.Size}}'\n405: ```\n406: \n407: ### 5.4 测试场景覆盖矩阵\n408: \n409: | Delta Spec 场景 | 测试方法 | 验证点 |\n410: |-----------------|----------|--------|\n411: | Builder 使用 Go 工具链 | 检查 Dockerfile 第一行 | `FROM golang:1.25-alpine` |\n412: | Builder 设置 CGO_ENABLED=0 | 检查 RUN go build 指令 | `CGO_ENABLED=0` 在环境变量中 |\n413: | 编译 workloadmanager 二进制 | 构建后检查 `/app/workloadmanager` | 文件存在且可执行 |\n414: | 运行时使用 Alpine 3.19 | 检查 Dockerfile 第二阶段 | `FROM alpine:3.19` |\n415: | COPY --from=builder 拷贝二进制 | 检查 COPY 指令 | 源路径匹配 builder 输出 |\n416: | 非 root 用户 apiserver (UID 1000) | `docker run id` | UID = 1000 |\n417: | EXPOSE 8080 (WM) | `docker inspect` | ExposedPorts 包含 8080 |\n418: | ENTRYPOINT 运行 workloadmanager | 容器启动日志 | 二进制正常启动 |\n419: | Router 编译包含 client-go | 检查 COPY 指令 | `COPY client-go/ client-go/` |\n420: | Router 非 root 用户 router (UID 1000) | `docker run id` | UID = 1000 |\n421: | PicoD 运行时包含 python3 | `docker run which python3` | python3 存在 |\n422: | PicoD 非 root 用户 (UID ≥ 1000) | `docker run id` | UID ≥ 1000 |\n423: | 构建上下文包含 go.mod/go.sum | 检查 COPY 指令 | `COPY go.mod go.sum ./` |\n424: | 运行时镜像无 Go 源码 | `docker run ls /workspace` | 目录不存在 |\n425: | 构建从干净 checkout 成功 | `docker build` 退出码 | 0 |\n426: | WM 镜像 /health 返回 200 | `curl /health` | HTTP 200 |\n427: | Router 镜像非 root 运行 | `docker run id` | UID ≠ 0 |\n428: | PicoD 镜像非 root 运行 | `docker run id` | UID ≠ 0 |\n429: \n430: ### 5.5 Makefile 集成测试\n431: \n432: ```bash\n433: # 验证 Makefile 目标使用正确的 Dockerfile\n434: make docker-build          # 应使用 docker/Dockerfile\n435: make docker-build-router   # 应使用 docker/Dockerfile.router\n436: make docker-build-picod    # 应使用 docker/Dockerfile.picod\n437: \n438: # 验证镜像标签正确\n439: docker image ls | grep workloadmanager  # 应显示 workloadmanager:latest\n440: docker image ls | grep agentcube-router # 应显示 agentcube-router:latest\n441: docker image ls | grep picod            # 应显示 picod:latest\n442: ```\n443: \n444: ---\n445: \n446: ## 6. 实现步骤 (Implementation Steps)\n447: \n448: ### 6.1 文件创建顺序\n449: \n450: | 步骤 | 操作 | 文件 | 说明 | 前置依赖 |\n451: |------|------|------|------|----------|\n452: | 1 | Create | `docker/` | 创建 docker 目录 | 无 |\n453: | 2 | Create | `docker/.dockerignore` | 排除非构建文件 | 步骤 1 |\n454: | 3 | Create | `docker/Dockerfile` | Workload Manager 多阶段构建 | 步骤 1 |\n455: | 4 | Create | `docker/Dockerfile.router` | Router 多阶段构建 (含 client-go COPY) | 步骤 1 |\n456: | 5 | Create | `docker/Dockerfile.picod` | PicoD 多阶段构建 (含 python3) | 步骤 1 |\n457: | 6 | Verify | — | 三个镜像构建成功 | 步骤 3-5 |\n458: | 7 | Verify | — | 运行时测试通过 (非 root, 健康检查) | 步骤 6 |\n459: \n460: ### 6.2 并行化分组 (Parallelizable Groups)\n461: \n462: | 组 | 任务 | 说明 |\n463: |----|------|------|\n464: | G1 | 步骤 1-2 (创建 docker/ 和 .dockerignore) | 独立创建，无依赖 |\n465: | G2 | 步骤 3, 4, 5 (三个 Dockerfile) | 可并行创建，都依赖 G1 (目录存在) |\n466: | G3 | 步骤 6-7 (构建和验证) | 依赖 G2 完成 (Dockerfile 已创建) |\n467: \n468: ### 6.3 验证检查清单 (Verification Checklist)\n469: \n470: - [ ] `docker/` 目录存在\n471: - [ ] `docker/.dockerignore` 排除 `.git`, `test/`, `testing/`, `sdk-python/`, `docs/`\n472: - [ ] `docker/Dockerfile` 使用 `golang:1.25-alpine` builder + `alpine:3.19` runtime\n473: - [ ] `docker/Dockerfile` 编译 `./cmd/workloadmanager`，输出 `workloadmanager`\n474: - [ ] `docker/Dockerfile` 创建用户 `apiserver` (UID 1000)，`USER apiserver`\n475: - [ ] `docker/Dockerfile` 包含 `EXPOSE 8080` 和 `ENTRYPOINT [\"/app/workloadmanager\"]`\n476: - [ ] `docker/Dockerfile.router` 额外 COPY `client-go/ client-go/`\n477: - [ ] `docker/Dockerfile.router` 编译 `./cmd/router`，输出 `agentcube-router`\n478: - [ ] `docker/Dockerfile.router` 创建用户 `router` (UID 1000)，`USER router`\n479: - [ ] `docker/Dockerfile.router` 包含 `EXPOSE 8080` 和 `ENTRYPOINT [\"/app/agentcube-router\"]`\n480: - [ ] `docker/Dockerfile.picod` 编译 `./cmd/picod`，输出 `picod`\n481: - [ ] `docker/Dockerfile.picod` 运行时安装 `python3`\n482: - [ ] `docker/Dockerfile.picod` 创建非 root 用户 (UID ≥ 1000)\n483: - [ ] `docker/Dockerfile.picod` ENTRYPOINT 为 `[\"/app/picod\"]`\n484: - [ ] 三个 Dockerfile 均使用 `CGO_ENABLED=0` 和 `-ldflags=\"-s -w\"`\n485: - [ ] 三个 Dockerfile 均使用 `GOOS=${TARGETOS} GOARCH=${TARGETARCH}`\n486: - [ ] `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile -t wm:test .` 成功\n487: - [ ] `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.router -t router:test .` 成功\n488: - [ ] `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.picod -t picod:test .` 成功\n489: - [ ] 三个镜像运行时 UID 均为 1000\n490: - [ ] WM 镜像 `/health` 返回 HTTP 200\n491: - [ ] Router 镜像 `/health/live` 返回 HTTP 200\n492: - [ ] 镜像中不包含 Go 工具链或源码\n493: \n494: ---\n495: \n496: ## 7. 后续变更 (Follow-up Changes)\n497: \n498: | 变更 | 依赖关系 | 说明 |\n499: |------|----------|------|\n500: | AgentD Dockerfile | 依赖本 AR 完成 | `cmd/agentd` 需要独立的 Dockerfile，遵循相同的多阶段构建模式 |\n501: | 镜像 digest 固定 | 独立 | 生产环境将 `alpine:3.19` 和 `golang:1.25-alpine` 替换为 digest-pinned 版本 |\n502: | 多架构构建 (buildx) | 依赖本 AR 完成 | Makefile `docker-buildx` 目标需适配新 Dockerfile 路径 |\n503: | 镜像推送 (CI/CD) | 依赖本 AR 完成 | CI 流水线构建并推送三个镜像到 `ghcr.io/volcano-sh/` |\n504: | 安全扫描集成 | 独立 | CI 中集成 Trivy/Grype 扫描三个镜像的 CVE |\n505: | 镜像大小优化 | 独立 | 评估使用 `distroless` 或 `scratch` 进一步减小镜像体积 |\n506: | Helm chart 镜像引用更新 | 依赖本 AR 完成 | `values.yaml` 中 `image.repository` 指向正确的 registry 路径 |\n\n(End of file - total 506 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-032: Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images) — Design/设计说明\n\n## 1. 架构 (Architecture)\n\n### 1.1 定位 (Purpose/Positioning)\n\n本变更为 AgentCube 项目创建三个独立的多阶段 Dockerfile，用于构建生产级容器镜像：\n\n| Dockerfile | 二进制 | 用途 |\n|------------|--------|------|\n| `docker/Dockerfile` | `workloadmanager` | Workload Manager — Kubernetes 控制器，管理 agent-sandbox 沙箱生命周期 |\n| `docker/Dockerfile.router` | `agentcube-router` | Router — HTTP 反向代理/会话路由器，将请求路由到正确的沙箱 |\n| `docker/Dockerfile.picod` | `picod` | PicoD — 沙箱内执行守护进程，负责代码解释器会话管理 |\n\n每个 Dockerfile 遵循统一的多阶段构建模式：Go 编译阶段 → 最小运行时阶段。构建产物为静态链接的二进制文件（`CGO_ENABLED=0`），运行时镜像仅包含 Alpine 3.19 基础层和编译后的二进制，不包含 Go 工具链、源码或构建缓存。\n\n### 1.2 目录结构 (Directory Layout)\n\n**当前状态 (Before):**\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-032/design.md","time":{"start":1775875941861,"end":1775875941871}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775875943234,"sessionID":"ses_2858e9b85ffetfq8oC43JXMakK","part":{"id":"prt_d7a746670001DYaNpWp0Bdk0A8","messageID":"msg_d7a7458fe001EP9qZCZ4T7mW2J","sessionID":"ses_2858e9b85ffetfq8oC43JXMakK","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_4457476eb98d45f1bed2f943","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-032/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-032/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-032: Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images) — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Context\n4: \n5: - **Module:** `docker`\n6: - **Language:** Dockerfile\n7: - **Size:** S\n8: - **Base specs:** `deployment/spec.md` (Requirement: Docker images for core binaries)\n9: \n10: ## Delta Requirements\n11: \n12: ### Requirement: Workload Manager Dockerfile (multi-stage)\n13: \n14: The system SHALL provide `docker/Dockerfile` that builds the Workload Manager binary via a multi-stage Docker build: a Go builder stage compiles `cmd/workloadmanager` with `CGO_ENABLED=0`, and a minimal runtime stage copies the binary into an Alpine 3.19 image running as non-root user `apiserver` (UID 1000), exposing port 8080.\n15: \n16: #### Scenario: Builder stage uses Go toolchain\n17: - **GIVEN** `docker/Dockerfile` is invoked with the repository root as build context\n18: - **WHEN** the first (builder) stage is evaluated\n19: - **THEN** it SHALL use a Go base image (e.g. `golang:1.25-alpine`) and set `CGO_ENABLED=0` in the build environment\n20: \n21: #### Scenario: Builder stage compiles workloadmanager binary\n22: - **GIVEN** the builder stage has the repository source available\n23: - **WHEN** `go build` runs\n24: - **THEN** it SHALL compile `./cmd/workloadmanager` and produce a static Linux binary at `/workloadmanager` (or equivalent output path)\n25: \n26: #### Scenario: Runtime stage uses Alpine 3.19\n27: - **GIVEN** the second (runtime) stage in `docker/Dockerfile`\n28: - **WHEN** the base image is inspected\n29: - **THEN** it SHALL be `alpine:3.19` (or a digest-pinned equivalent)\n30: \n31: #### Scenario: Binary is copied from builder to runtime\n32: - **GIVEN** both stages exist in `docker/Dockerfile`\n33: - **WHEN** the `COPY --from=builder` instruction is evaluated\n34: - **THEN** it SHALL copy the compiled `workloadmanager` binary from the builder stage into the runtime image\n35: \n36: #### Scenario: Non-root user apiserver is created\n37: - **GIVEN** the runtime stage\n38: - **WHEN** the image is built\n39: - **THEN** it SHALL create a user `apiserver` with UID 1000 and set `USER apiserver` as the active user\n40: \n41: #### Scenario: Port 8080 is exposed\n42: - **GIVEN** the runtime stage\n43: - **WHEN** the image metadata is inspected\n44: - **THEN** `EXPOSE 8080` SHALL be present\n45: \n46: #### Scenario: Entrypoint runs the workloadmanager binary\n47: - **GIVEN** a container launched from the built image\n48: - **WHEN** the container starts\n49: - **THEN** it SHALL execute the `workloadmanager` binary (via `ENTRYPOINT` or `CMD`)\n50: \n51: ### Requirement: Router Dockerfile (multi-stage)\n52: \n53: The system SHALL provide `docker/Dockerfile.router` that builds the Router binary via a multi-stage Docker build: a Go builder stage compiles `cmd/router` with `CGO_ENABLED=0`, and a minimal runtime stage copies the binary into an Alpine 3.19 image running as non-root user `router` (UID 1000), exposing port 8080.\n54: \n55: #### Scenario: Builder stage compiles router binary\n56: - **GIVEN** `docker/Dockerfile.router` is invoked with the repository root as build context\n57: - **WHEN** the builder stage runs `go build`\n58: - **THEN** it SHALL compile `./cmd/router` with `CGO_ENABLED=0` and produce a static Linux binary\n59: \n60: #### Scenario: Runtime stage uses Alpine 3.19\n61: - **GIVEN** the runtime stage in `docker/Dockerfile.router`\n62: - **WHEN** the base image is inspected\n63: - **THEN** it SHALL be `alpine:3.19` (or a digest-pinned equivalent)\n64: \n65: #### Scenario: Non-root user router is created\n66: - **GIVEN** the runtime stage\n67: - **WHEN** the image is built\n68: - **THEN** it SHALL create a user `router` with UID 1000 and set `USER router` as the active user\n69: \n70: #### Scenario: Port 8080 is exposed\n71: - **GIVEN** the runtime stage\n72: - **WHEN** the image metadata is inspected\n73: - **THEN** `EXPOSE 8080` SHALL be present\n74: \n75: #### Scenario: Entrypoint runs the router binary\n76: - **GIVEN** a container launched from the built image\n77: - **WHEN** the container starts\n78: - **THEN** it SHALL execute the `router` binary (via `ENTRYPOINT` or `CMD`)\n79: \n80: ### Requirement: PicoD Dockerfile (multi-stage)\n81: \n82: The system SHALL provide `docker/Dockerfile.picod` that builds the PicoD daemon binary via a multi-stage Docker build: a Go builder stage compiles `cmd/picod` with `CGO_ENABLED=0`, and a minimal runtime stage copies the binary into an Alpine 3.19 image running as a non-root user, suitable for execution inside sandbox pods.\n83: \n84: #### Scenario: Builder stage compiles picod binary\n85: - **GIVEN** `docker/Dockerfile.picod` is invoked with the repository root as build context\n86: - **WHEN** the builder stage runs `go build`\n87: - **THEN** it SHALL compile `./cmd/picod` with `CGO_ENABLED=0` and produce a static Linux binary\n88: \n89: #### Scenario: Runtime stage uses Alpine 3.19\n90: - **GIVEN** the runtime stage in `docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n91: - **WHEN** the base image is inspected\n92: - **THEN** it SHALL be `alpine:3.19` (or a digest-pinned equivalent)\n93: \n94: #### Scenario: Non-root user is configured\n95: - **GIVEN** the runtime stage\n96: - **WHEN** the image is built\n97: - **THEN** it SHALL create a non-root user (UID ≥ 1000) and set it as the active user via `USER`\n98: \n99: #### Scenario: Entrypoint runs the picod binary\n100: - **GIVEN** a container launched from the built image\n101: - **WHEN** the container starts\n102: - **THEN** it SHALL execute the `picod` binary (via `ENTRYPOINT` or `CMD`)\n103: \n104: ### Requirement: Build context and reproducibility\n105: \n106: All three Dockerfiles SHALL use the repository root as build context and produce deterministic, minimal images suitable for production deployment.\n107: \n108: #### Scenario: Build context includes Go module files\n109: - **GIVEN** `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile .` is run from the repository root\n110: - **WHEN** the builder stage resolves dependencies\n111: - **THEN** `go.mod` and `go.sum` SHALL be available for `go mod download` before source code is copied (layer caching optimization)\n112: \n113: #### Scenario: No unnecessary files in runtime image\n114: - **GIVEN** a built image from any of the three Dockerfiles\n115: - **WHEN** the image filesystem is inspected\n116: - **THEN** it SHALL NOT contain Go source code, build caches, or the Go toolchain — only the compiled binary, Alpine base packages, and the non-root user home directory\n117: \n118: #### Scenario: Image builds succeed from clean checkout\n119: - **GIVEN** a clean clone of the repository at the correct commit\n120: - **WHEN** `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile -t workloadmanager:test .` is executed\n121: - **THEN** the build SHALL complete with exit code 0 and produce a valid image\n122: \n123: ### Requirement: Docker build output integrity\n124: \n125: Each built image SHALL contain a working binary that starts and responds to its health endpoint (where applicable).\n126: \n127: #### Scenario: Workload Manager image responds to /health\n128: - **GIVEN** a container running from the Workload Manager image with default configuration\n129: - **WHEN** an HTTP GET request is sent to `http://localhost:8080/health`\n130: - **THEN** the response SHALL return HTTP 200 OK\n131: \n132: #### Scenario: Router image starts without root privileges\n133: - **GIVEN** a container running from the Router image\n134: - **WHEN** the container's effective UID is inspected\n135: - **THEN** it SHALL be 1000 (the `router` user), not 0 (root)\n136: \n137: #### Scenario: PicoD image starts without root privileges\n138: - **GIVEN** a container running from the PicoD image\n139: - **WHEN** the container's effective UID is inspected\n140: - **THEN** it SHALL be ≥ 1000 (non-root user), not 0 (root)\n141: \n142: ---\n143: \n144: ## File Changes\n145: \n146: | Action | File | Description |\n147: |--------|------|-------------|\n148: | Create | `docker/Dockerfile` | Multi-stage build for Workload Manager (Go builder → Alpine 3.19, non-root `apiserver`) |\n149: | Create | `docker/Dockerfile.router` | Multi-stage build for Router (Go builder → Alpine 3.19, non-root `router`) |\n150: | Create | `docker/Dockerfile.picod` | Multi-stage build for PicoD daemon (Go builder → Alpine 3.19, non-root user) |\n151: | Create | `docker/.dockerignore` | Exclude `.git`, `test/`, `sdk-python/`, `docs/`, and other non-build artifacts from Docker context |\n\n(End of file - total 151 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-032: Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images) — Delta Spec\n\n## Context\n\n- **Module:** `docker`\n- **Language:** Dockerfile\n- **Size:** S\n- **Base specs:** `deployment/spec.md` (Requirement: Docker images for core binaries)\n\n## Delta Requirements\n\n### Requirement: Workload Manager Dockerfile (multi-stage)\n\nThe system SHALL provide `docker/Dockerfile` that builds the Workload Manager binary via a multi-stage Docker build: a Go builder stage compiles `cmd/workloadmanager` with `CGO_ENABLED=0`, and a minimal runtime stage copies the binary into an Alpine 3.19 image running as non-root user `apiserver` (UID 1000), exposing port 8080.\n\n#### Scenario: Builder stage uses Go toolchain\n- **GIVEN** `docker/Dockerfile` is invoked with the repository root as build context\n- **WHEN** the first (builder) stage is evaluated\n- **THEN** it SHALL use a Go base image (e.g. `golang:1.25-alpine`) and set `CGO_ENABLED=0` in the build environment\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-032/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775875943226,"end":1775875943233}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775875944600,"sessionID":"ses_2858e9b85ffetfq8oC43JXMakK","part":{"id":"prt_d7a746bc70016qPI0Xb78yWMyo","messageID":"msg_d7a7458fe001EP9qZCZ4T7mW2J","sessionID":"ses_2858e9b85ffetfq8oC43JXMakK","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_12323a1a15ff463dbefd3c63","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-032/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-032/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-032 — Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images) — Tasks\n2: \n3: > **Module:** docker\n4: > **Language:** Dockerfile\n5: > **Size:** S\n6: > **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n7: > **Reference:** `changes/AR-032/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-032/design.md`, `changes/AR-032/delta-spec.md`\n8: > **Dependency:** None (greenfield — `docker/` directory does not exist yet)\n9: \n10: ---\n11: \n12: ## T-001: 创建 docker/ 目录与 .dockerignore\n13: \n14: - [ ] T-001.01 创建 `docker/` 目录\n15: - [ ] T-001.02 创建 `docker/.dockerignore`，排除 `.git`、`.gitignore`、`test/`、`testing/`、`sdk-python/`、`docs/`、`coverage.out`、`.pytest_cache/`、`.coverage`、`*.md`（保留 `!README.md`）\n16: \n17: **验收**: `ls docker/.dockerignore` 文件存在；`grep -c \"\\.git\" docker/.dockerignore` ≥ 1；`grep -c \"test/\" docker/.dockerignore` ≥ 1\n18: \n19: ---\n20: \n21: ## T-002: Workload Manager Dockerfile (docker/Dockerfile)\n22: \n23: - [ ] T-002.01 Stage 1 (builder): `FROM golang:1.25-alpine AS builder`，设置 `WORKDIR /workspace`\n24: - [ ] T-002.02 Builder: `COPY go.mod go.sum ./` 后 `RUN go mod download`（层缓存优化）\n25: - [ ] T-002.03 Builder: `COPY cmd/ cmd/` 和 `COPY pkg/ pkg/`\n26: - [ ] T-002.04 Builder: `RUN CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=${TARGETOS} GOARCH=${TARGETARCH} go build -ldflags=\"-s -w\" -o /workloadmanager ./cmd/workloadmanager`\n27: - [ ] T-002.05 Stage 2 (runtime): `FROM alpine:3.19`，`RUN apk add --no-cache ca-certificates`\n28: - [ ] T-002.06 Runtime: `WORKDIR /app`，`COPY --from=builder /workloadmanager /app/workloadmanager`\n29: - [ ] T-002.07 Runtime: `RUN adduser -D -u 1000 apiserver`，`USER apiserver`\n30: - [ ] T-002.08 Runtime: `EXPOSE 8080`，`ENTRYPOINT [\"/app/workloadmanager\"]`，`CMD [\"--port=8080\"]`\n31: \n32: **验收**: `grep -c \"FROM golang:1.25-alpine\" docker/Dockerfile` → 1；`grep -c \"FROM alpine:3.19\" docker/Dockerfile` → 1；`grep \"CGO_ENABLED=0\" docker/Dockerfile` 有输出；`grep \"adduser.*1000 apiserver\" docker/Dockerfile` 有输出；`grep \"EXPOSE 8080\" docker/Dockerfile` 有输出；`grep 'ENTRYPOINT' docker/Dockerfile` 含 `/app/workloadmanager`\n33: \n34: ---\n35: \n36: ## T-003: Router Dockerfile (docker/Dockerfile.router)\n37: \n38: - [ ] T-003.01 Stage 1 (builder): `FROM golang:1.25-alpine AS builder`，设置 `WORKDIR /workspace`\n39: - [ ] T-003.02 Builder: `COPY go.mod go.sum ./` 后 `RUN go mod download`\n40: - [ ] T-003.03 Builder: `COPY cmd/ cmd/`、`COPY pkg/ pkg/`、`COPY client-go/ client-go/`\n41: - [ ] T-003.04 Builder: `RUN CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=${TARGETOS} GOARCH=${TARGETARCH} go build -ldflags=\"-s -w\" -o /agentcube-router ./cmd/router`\n42: - [ ] T-003.05 Stage 2 (runtime): `FROM alpine:3.19`，`RUN apk add --no-cache ca-certificates`\n43: - [ ] T-003.06 Runtime: `WORKDIR /app`，`COPY --from=builder /agentcube-router /app/agentcube-router`\n44: - [ ] T-003.07 Runtime: `RUN adduser -D -u 1000 router`，`USER router`\n45: - [ ] T-003.08 Runtime: `EXPOSE 8080`，`ENTRYPOINT [\"/app/agentcube-router\"]`，`CMD [\"--port=8080\", \"--debug\"]`\n46: \n47: **验收**: `grep -c \"FROM golang:1.25-alpine\" docker/Dockerfile.router` → 1；`grep -c \"FROM alpine:3.19\" docker/Dockerfile.router` → 1；`grep \"COPY client-go/\" docker/Dockerfile.router` 有输出；`grep \"CGO_ENABLED=0\" docker/Dockerfile.router` 有输出；`grep \"adduser.*1000 router\" docker/Dockerfile.router` 有输出；`grep \"EXPOSE 8080\" docker/Dockerfile.router` 有输出；`grep 'ENTRYPOINT' docker/Dockerfile.router` 含 `/app/agentcube-router`\n48: \n49: ---\n50: \n51: ## T-004: PicoD Dockerfile (docker/Dockerfile.picod)\n52: \n53: - [ ] T-004.01 Stage 1 (builder): `FROM golang:1.25-alpine AS builder`，设置 `WORKDIR /workspace`\n54: - [ ] T-004.02 Builder: `COPY go.mod go.sum ./` 后 `RUN go mod download`\n55: - [ ] T-004.03 Builder: `COPY cmd/ cmd/`、`COPY pkg/ pkg/`\n56: - [ ] T-004.04 Builder: `RUN CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=${TARGETOS} GOARCH=${TARGETARCH} go build -ldflags=\"-s -w\" -o /picod ./cmd/picod`\n57: - [ ] T-004.05 Stage 2 (runtime): `FROM alpine:3.19`，`RUN apk add --no-cache python3`\n58: - [ ] T-004.06 Runtime: `WORKDIR /app`，`COPY --from=builder /picod /app/picod`\n59: - [ ] T-004.07 Runtime: `RUN adduser -D -u 1000 picod`，`USER picod`\n60: - [ ] T-004.08 Runtime: `ENTRYPOINT [\"/app/picod\"]`（无 EXPOSE，无 CMD）\n61: \n62: **验收**: `grep -c \"FROM golang:1.25-alpine\" docker/Dockerfile.picod` → 1；`grep -c \"FROM alpine:3.19\" docker/Dockerfile.picod` → 1；`grep \"CGO_ENABLED=0\" docker/Dockerfile.picod` 有输出；`grep \"apk add.*python3\" docker/Dockerfile.picod` 有输出；`grep \"adduser.*1000 picod\" docker/Dockerfile.picod` 有输出；`grep \"EXPOSE\" docker/Dockerfile.picod` 无输出；`grep 'ENTRYPOINT' docker/Dockerfile.picod` 含 `/app/picod`\n63: \n64: ---\n65: \n66: ## T-005: 三镜像构建验证\n67: \n68: - [ ] T-005.01 `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile -t wm:test .` 成功（退出码 0）\n69: - [ ] T-005.02 `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.router -t router:test .` 成功（退出码 0）\n70: - [ ] T-005.03 `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.picod -t picod:test .` 成功（退出码 0）\n71: \n72: **验收**: 三条 `docker build` 命令均退出码 0；`docker image ls | grep -E \"wm:test|router:test|picod:test\"` 显示三个镜像\n73: \n74: ---\n75: \n76: ## T-006: 镜像内容静态验证\n77: \n78: - [ ] T-006.01 三个镜像均不包含 Go 工具链：`docker run --rm <image> which go` 返回非 0\n79: - [ ] T-006.02 WM 镜像含二进制：`docker run --rm wm:test ls -la /app/workloadmanager` 有输出\n80: - [ ] T-006.03 Router 镜像含二进制：`docker run --rm router:test ls -la /app/agentcube-router` 有输出\n81: - [ ] T-006.04 PicoD 镜像含二进制：`docker run --rm picod:test ls -la /app/picod` 有输出\n82: - [ ] T-006.05 PicoD 镜像含 python3：`docker run --rm picod:test which python3` 有输出\n83: - [ ] T-006.06 WM/Router 镜像含 ca-certificates：`docker run --rm wm:test ls /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt` 有输出\n84: \n85: **验收**: T-006.01 三个镜像 `which go` 均失败；T-006.02~006.04 二进制文件均存在；T-006.05 `which python3` 在 picod 镜像中返回路径；T-006.06 ca-certificates 文件存在于 WM/Router 镜像\n86: \n87: ---\n88: \n89: ## T-007: 非 root 用户验证\n90: \n91: - [ ] T-007.01 WM 镜像运行 UID = 1000：`docker run --rm wm:test id -u` 输出 `1000`\n92: - [ ] T-007.02 Router 镜像运行 UID = 1000：`docker run --rm router:test id -u` 输出 `1000`\n93: - [ ] T-007.03 PicoD 镜像运行 UID = 1000：`docker run --rm picod:test id -u` 输出 `1000`\n94: \n95: **验收**: 三条 `docker run --rm <image> id -u` 均输出 `1000`\n96: \n97: ---\n98: \n99: ## T-008: 端口暴露与入口点验证\n100: \n101: - [ ] T-008.01 WM 镜像 ExposedPorts 含 8080：`docker inspect wm:test --format='{{json .Config.ExposedPorts}}'` 含 `\"8080/tcp\"`\n102: - [ ] T-008.02 Router 镜像 ExposedPorts 含 8080：`docker inspect router:test --format='{{json .Config.ExposedPorts}}'` 含 `\"8080/tcp\"`\n103: - [ ] T-008.03 PicoD 镜像无 ExposedPorts：`docker inspect picod:test --format='{{json .Config.ExposedPorts}}'` 输出 `null` 或 `{}`\n104: - [ ] T-008.04 WM 镜像 Entrypoint 为 `/app/workloadmanager`：`docker inspect wm:test --format='{{json .Config.Entrypoint}}'` 含 `/app/workloadmanager`\n105: - [ ] T-008.05 Router 镜像 Entrypoint 为 `/app/agentcube-router`：`docker inspect router:test --format='{{json .Config.Entrypoint}}'` 含 `/app/agentcube-router`\n106: - [ ] T-008.06 PicoD 镜像 Entrypoint 为 `/app/picod`：`docker inspect picod:test --format='{{json .Config.Entrypoint}}'` 含 `/app/picod`\n107: \n108: **验收**: 六个 `docker inspect` 命令输出均符合预期\n109: \n110: ---\n111: \n112: ## T-009: 镜像大小验证\n113: \n114: - [ ] T-009.01 WM 镜像大小 < 50 MB\n115: - [ ] T-009.02 Router 镜像大小 < 50 MB\n116: - [ ] T-009.03 PicoD 镜像大小 < 100 MB（含 python3）\n117: \n118: **验收**: `docker image inspect wm:test --format='{{.Size}}'` 输出 < 52428800；`docker image inspect router:test --format='{{.Size}}'` 输出 < 52428800；`docker image inspect picod:test --format='{{.Size}}'` 输出 < 104857600\n119: \n120: ---\n121: \n122: ## T-010: 目录结构最终验证\n123: \n124: - [ ] T-010.01 `docker/` 目录包含 `Dockerfile`、`Dockerfile.router`、`Dockerfile.picod`、`.dockerignore` 四个文件\n125: - [ ] T-010.02 三个 Dockerfile 均使用两阶段构建（`FROM ... AS builder` + `FROM alpine:3.19`）\n126: - [ ] T-010.03 三个 Dockerfile 均包含 `-ldflags=\"-s -w\"` 编译标志\n127: - [ ] T-010.04 三个 Dockerfile 均包含 `GOOS=${TARGETOS} GOARCH=${TARGETARCH}` 跨平台支持\n128: \n129: **验收**: `ls docker/` 输出四个文件；`grep -l \"FROM.*AS builder\" docker/Dockerfile*` 匹配三个文件；`grep -l 'ldflags=\"-s -w\"' docker/Dockerfile*` 匹配三个文件；`grep -l \"GOOS=\\${TARGETOS}\" docker/Dockerfile*` 匹配三个文件\n130: \n131: ---\n132: \n133: ## Dependency Graph\n134: \n135: ```\n136: T-001 (docker/ + .dockerignore) ──┬── T-002 (WM Dockerfile) ──┐\n137:                                    ├── T-003 (Router Dockerfile)├── T-005 (build all 3)\n138:                                    └── T-004 (PicoD Dockerfile) ┤\n139:                                                               ├── T-006 (content verify)\n140:                                                               ├── T-007 (non-root verify)\n141:                                                               ├── T-008 (ports/entrypoint)\n142:                                                               ├── T-009 (size verify)\n143:                                                               └── T-010 (structure verify)\n144: ```\n145: \n146: ## Parallelizable Groups\n147: \n148: | Group | Tasks | Prerequisites |\n149: |-------|-------|---------------|\n150: | G1 | T-001 (docker/ + .dockerignore) | None |\n151: | G2 | T-002 (WM), T-003 (Router), T-004 (PicoD) | G1 |\n152: | G3 | T-005 (build all 3) | G2 |\n153: | G4 | T-006 (content), T-007 (non-root), T-008 (ports), T-009 (size), T-010 (structure) | G3 |\n154: \n155: ---\n156: \n157: ## Acceptance Criteria\n158: \n159: | # | Criterion | Command |\n160: |---|-----------|---------|\n161: | AC1 | `docker/` 目录存在且含 4 个文件 | `ls docker/` 输出 `Dockerfile Dockerfile.router Dockerfile.picod .dockerignore` |\n162: | AC2 | .dockerignore 排除 `.git`、`test/`、`docs/` | `grep -c \"\\.git\\|test/\\|docs/\" docker/.dockerignore` ≥ 3 |\n163: | AC3 | WM Dockerfile 使用 golang:1.25-alpine + alpine:3.19 | `grep \"FROM golang:1.25-alpine\" docker/Dockerfile` && `grep \"FROM alpine:3.19\" docker/Dockerfile` |\n164: | AC4 | WM Dockerfile 编译 ./cmd/workloadmanager，CGO_ENABLED=0 | `grep \"CGO_ENABLED=0.*workloadmanager\" docker/Dockerfile` |\n165: | AC5 | WM Dockerfile 创建 apiserver (UID 1000)，EXPOSE 8080 | `grep \"adduser.*1000 apiserver\" docker/Dockerfile` && `grep \"EXPOSE 8080\" docker/Dockerfile` |\n166: | AC6 | Router Dockerfile 额外 COPY client-go/ | `grep \"COPY client-go/\" docker/Dockerfile.router` |\n167: | AC7 | Router Dockerfile 创建 router (UID 1000)，EXPOSE 8080 | `grep \"adduser.*1000 router\" docker/Dockerfile.router` && `grep \"EXPOSE 8080\" docker/Dockerfile.router` |\n168: | AC8 | PicoD Dockerfile 安装 python3，无 EXPOSE | `grep \"apk add.*python3\" docker/Dockerfile.picod` && `! grep \"EXPOSE\" docker/Dockerfile.picod` |\n169: | AC9 | PicoD Dockerfile 创建 picod (UID 1000) | `grep \"adduser.*1000 picod\" docker/Dockerfile.picod` |\n170: | AC10 | 三镜像构建成功 | `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile -t wm:test .` && `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.router -t router:test .` && `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.picod -t picod:test .` 均退出码 0 |\n171: | AC11 | 三镜像无 Go 工具链 | `docker run --rm wm:test which go \\|\\| true` 无输出；Router/PicoD 同理 |\n172: | AC12 | 三镜像运行时 UID = 1000 | `docker run --rm wm:test id -u` → 1000；Router/PicoD 同理 |\n173: | AC13 | WM/Router EXPOSE 8080，PicoD 无 | `docker inspect wm:test --format='{{json .Config.ExposedPorts}}'` 含 8080；PicoD 为 null |\n174: | AC14 | WM 镜像 < 50MB，Router < 50MB，PicoD < 100MB | `docker image inspect <image> --format='{{.Size}}'` 分别验证 |\n175: | AC15 | 三 Dockerfile 均含 -ldflags=\"-s -w\" | `grep -l 'ldflags=\"-s -w\"' docker/Dockerfile*` 匹配 3 个文件 |\n176: | AC16 | 三 Dockerfile 均含跨平台构建支持 | `grep -l 'GOOS=\\${TARGETOS}' docker/Dockerfile*` 匹配 3 个文件 |\n\n(End of file - total 176 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-032 — Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images) — Tasks\n\n> **Module:** docker\n> **Language:** Dockerfile\n> **Size:** S\n> **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n> **Reference:** `changes/AR-032/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-032/design.md`, `changes/AR-032/delta-spec.md`\n> **Dependency:** None (greenfield — `docker/` directory does not exist yet)\n\n---\n\n## T-001: 创建 docker/ 目录与 .dockerignore\n\n- [ ] T-001.01 创建 `docker/` 目录\n- [ ] T-001.02 创建 `docker/.dockerignore`，排除 `.git`、`.gitignore`、`test/`、`testing/`、`sdk-python/`、`docs/`、`coverage.out`、`.pytest_cache/`、`.coverage`、`*.md`（保留 `!README.md`）\n\n**验收**: `ls docker/.dockerignore` 文件存在；`grep -c \"\\.git\" docker/.dockerignore` ≥ 1；`grep -c \"test/\" docker/.dockerignore` ≥ 1\n\n---\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-032/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775875944592,"end":1775875944598}}}}
